Name: ZIPPO GROUP
Explanation: A COLLECTION OF ANTI-SHIP MISSILE DEFENCE MEASURES, EITHER PREDEFINED IN ATP-55/EXTAC 417 OR ESTABLISHED ON AN AD-HOC BASIS FOR A SPECIFIC OPERATION. DOCTRINE RELATING TO THIS FUD IS NATO SECRET, SO CARE MUST BE TAKEN WITH ASSOCIATED EXPLANATIONS AND EXAMPLES TO AVOID ADATP-3 SECURITY MARKINGS HIGHER THAN NATO UNCLASSIFIED.
